{"tid":2020728,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大外宣】一文比你睇哂邊間PR接咗job幫香港政府洗底","createTime":"2020-05-17T09:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T14:41:16.000Z","uid":89663,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f8b54c3bd454a7f5e5978c7cfc470a9e37dcf1","tid":2020728,"uid":89663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"今日喺Twitter睇到有人post咗一篇新聞，但似乎無幾多人留意到呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n重點係入面<span style=\"color: red;\">有幾間係美國世界級PR公司</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住啲公司投完個標奶完之後仲講埋啲冠冕堂皇嘅說話，真係令人作嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要煲大件事又好，廣傳比外國政府官員同議員知又好，點做都好，各位巴絲可以從長計議。小弟廢事亂咁指點了，但希望大家最少有個知字先。不過根據報道（第11段），今次政府支PR標係包裝成「重振經濟」，用經濟做擋箭牌，嘗試同淋病同埋政治議題分割，大家可能需要留意一下。<br />\n<br />\n下低小弟會盡量翻譯同整理篇報道。長篇放後面，比定啲傳送門大家先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Tweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/george_chen/status/1261486311271088129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgeorge_chen%2Fstatus%2F1261486311271088129&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e614nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=cb0c3541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgeorge_chen%2Fstatus%2F1261486311271088129&h=b979c335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/george_chen/status/1261486311271088129</a> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> PRovoke（前身係The Holmes Report）報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.provokemedia.com/latest/article/edelman-steps-up-as-global-pr-firms-again-steer-clear-of-hong-kong-government\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.provokemedia.com%2Flatest%2Farticle%2Fedelman-steps-up-as-global-pr-firms-again-steer-clear-of-hong-kong-government&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e614nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=04e6f2e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.provokemedia.com/latest/article/edelman-steps-up-as-global-pr-firms-again-steer-clear-of-hong-kong-government</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外SCMP都有相關報道，可以用作參考睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3082326/hong-kong-government-turns-global-pr-firms-second-time\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3082326%2Fhong-kong-government-turns-global-pr-firms-second-time&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e614nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=88ff4657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3082326/hong-kong-government-turns-global-pr-firms-second-time</a>"},{"pid":"f7dca276519e65d9b7cbb594a40d24555e9023db","tid":2020728,"uid":89663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"為免大家睇英文too long didn't read，小弟試下用幾個鐘將篇報道翻譯同整合一下。戴返個頭盔，小弟唔係翻譯之材，背景資料都識得唔多，內容一概以相關報道為準，解錯恕不負責。如果有高手見到有錯漏唔該指點補充返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於投標公司</span><br />\n（第4-6, 21段）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Edelman<br />\n一間美國PR公司，亦係世界最大PR公司，員工數目接近7000人<br />\n發言人仲話「今次支標係去support香港嘅海外經濟，呢個議題對我地大家都好有影響，所以今次好高興我地有份提案。」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Qorvis/MSL<br />\n兩間係姊妹公司，總部設於美國華盛頓，兩間公司合作一齊簽咗一年<br />\nQorvis曾經喺911之後受沙地阿拉伯政府聘請去提升形象<br />\nMSL發言人拒絕評論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Redhill<br />\n總部設於新加坡，近年排名極速上升<br />\n<br />\n當然，政府新聞處自己係唔會報告有邊間同幾多間公司有參與過投標。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於其他PR公司反應</span><br />\n（第7-16段）<br />\n<br />\n其他國際級PR公司亦都有比正苦聯絡過，包括APCO, BCW, Crosby, Ogilvy, OPRG, Ruder Finn等等，但佢地一係拒絕投標一係無再回應正苦。當中Crosby上年社會運動期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">已經話過香港正苦應該針對示威成因去解決問題，而唔係單純去簡化做公關議題</span>。有公司亦形容<span style=\"color: red;\">香港正苦係一個充滿爭議嘅客</span>，表達擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n上年正苦搵公司洗底果陣，已經有意見擔心幫正苦做PR會<span style=\"color: red;\">影響公司信譽同本地員工</span>，質疑個job做唔做得過。至於今次招標，雖然focus喺經濟方面，寫明唔需要政治諮詢；但多間公司發現今次PR其實同上次分別不大，正苦今次大外宣個方向<span style=\"color: red;\">仍然係將事件歸咎於社會動亂</span>，所以接今次份job<span style=\"color: red;\">只會助長個政權鎮壓</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有本地公司都對幫正苦做野有保留，表示大家都想幫香港做啲野為香港好，但今時今日咁嘅環境，加上武漢肺炎爆發令不滿中国嘅情緒一直升溫，再幫正苦咁樣傳播信息並唔係一件完全正確嘅事。<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然支標個任務睇落好直接（主打經濟牌），但唔喺香港生活根本唔會知件事背後係想點。</span>早前有本地PR工會已經警告過，接呢啲正苦job到頭來只會等於走去幫個政權玩spin。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於政府支標</span><br />\n（第2, 8, 11, 18-20段）<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲有印象，可能會記得上年8月正苦已經蠢蠢欲動，想搵公關公司幫手洗底，但好彩開完簡報會，邀請8間公關公司，結果都係食檸檬，最後無公司落標。忘記咗嘅可以睇下蘋果報道： <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190918/VZNP7VACERS5HBSB7AU2SSEMAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190918%2FVZNP7VACERS5HBSB7AU2SSEMAQ%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e614nMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=6e6935ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190918%2FVZNP7VACERS5HBSB7AU2SSEMAQ%2F&h=e1ee2107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190918/VZNP7VACERS5HBSB7AU2SSEMAQ/</a> <br />\n<br />\n今次正苦捲土重來，經政府新聞處（ISD）用「Relaunch Hong Kong」之名重新邀請本地同外地PR公司參與投標，聲稱旨在「恢復香港『全球商業中心』嘅美譽」。同上次閉門邀請唔同，今次<span style=\"color: red;\">招標係公開</span>去做，而且<span style=\"color: red;\">降低咗中標公司要求</span>：公司需要喺香港有一間office同最少兩個員工，而且喺北美或者歐洲都要有office；但唔肯定中標公司可唔可以同本地公司合作去達到呢項要求。<br />\n<br />\n更重要嘅係，正如上面提及，今次招標雖然內裡套路同上次差唔多，但正苦深知直接攻擊示威係唔會有PR公司落搭，所以改變策略<span style=\"color: red;\">打經濟牌</span>，要求target國際公司，利用商界希望全世界救救香港經濟嘅聲音去做大外宣。<br />\n<br />\n政府為PR落咗幾重本？原來今年財政預算案中，已經<span style=\"color: red;\">預留咗二億二千六百幾萬</span>比新聞處做國際公關戰，比起上年多咗53.5%。原來淋病今年初去達沃斯世界經濟論壇果陣，承認<span style=\"color: red;\">政府公關機制過時</span>，暗示西方媒體煽動示威，<span style=\"color: red;\">受「世界級宣傳機器」挑戰</span>令自己民望下跌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可想而知今次肯揼幾多本錢去搞propaganda。報道亦有提過，由於現時<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟不景令好多公司生意陷入困境</span>，故此今次正苦一出重本再改變策略，就令一啲PR公司耳仔軟，甘願為呢個政權打工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔介意SCMP紅底，可以睇埋佢篇報道，內容大致上差不多，只係喺中標公司office要求、公關工作方向目標同策略，以及訪問學者同顧問幾方面深入少少。只可惜幾星期前蔡子強先斷估「無幾多間公司肯幫林鄭做野」，點知結果呢幾日就發現幾間知名大公司都落咗搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d22c4858cda494245213d310461ae8496e37b64","tid":2020728,"uid":89663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"上面講咗咁耐，整返個終極TLDR先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府新一輪大外宣計劃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豪洗二億二千幾萬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />轉換策略，主打經濟牌，利用外宣公關手法吸引外國企業投資香港做生意，重振香港經濟同建立香港聲譽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內裡實則換湯不換藥，仍然歸咎示威動亂，將香港深層政治問題簡化做公關問題去解決，唔知係咪同近期中聯辦主打嘅「黑暴攬炒論」有關<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已確定Edelman、Qorvis/MSL等等國際知名公關公司中標<br />\n<br />\n唔知將來輿輪機器會點樣做，但請大家繼續打國際線，時刻警惕。唔好比正苦spin走核心政治問題，唔好比propaganda帶到風向，令全世界以為係抗爭活動引致經濟衰退。大家一齊努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880c3bd5460f21959f43fcf94dcaaadb6bd16f4b","tid":2020728,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"入咗 未知邊個中"},{"pid":"6c85ecd5c1cc7d5f4d4206531046948148a1d363","tid":2020728,"uid":118330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80870bcd4010e5fae29bfd4116ce82da48d7de13","tid":2020728,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf76fd0fb2b4f97d091fd5d01c7ef49c5a985bb0","tid":2020728,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d699b2c3041f65c15a55c3c9486277147cbec72","tid":2020728,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺連登圍穩嗰間 PR 公司有冇入標呀 ?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲諗 ?  有閪資格咩你地 咁撚廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed82ba1f0ed59565224b485687f1868de1444fb0","tid":2020728,"uid":89663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"原來有巴打今日都出咗post講呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭招聘公關 有公司入紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2020426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2020426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ee1908dbc5be3e3cefaa3e3c81c9ca029b3e4ba","tid":2020728,"uid":304306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"PR手段<br />\n1. 扮yellownazi周圍屌人冇社運cv<br />\n2. 扮極端販粉周街賣熱狗<br />\n3. 扮熱狗屌販民不良記錄<br />\n4. 強行標籤 例: 唔撐販民就係熱普城<br />\n5. 建立大台制造公子獻頭環境 例: 大量不明所以嘅初選群組"},{"pid":"44d172498cff2845efc5acf51af0c93dafef9a5a","tid":2020728,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b35820512641652aaa1e5b7dcae68171c